name: Lollipop Chainsaw | Juliet Starling (Cheer Outfit)
description:
This LoRA is trained with 10 images, varying from cosplays to fan arts, of Juliet Starling from Lollipop Chainsaw in her standard Cheer Uniform.

Sadly AI still can't spell, so outfit is as close as I could get it.

Simply load up your favorite model and use <lora:juliet starling:1> for this lora to take effect!

This LoRA was trained using SD 1.5 and therefore may not work with all models!

For early access and custom LoRA's consider joining my patreon! https://patreon.com/Crazygirlashleyy
